    <!-- About screen -->
    <string name="title_activity_about">WTA. About</string>
    <string name="about_text">
        WatchThemAll is a series tracker app. Nowadays there are quite a lot of options regarding
        TV series, and sometimes it may be difficult to decide which series to watch and to be sure
        of not forgetting any episode of our favorite shows.\n\n
        This application aims to make all of that more easy to the user, at the same time that
        makes the hobby of watching and following TV series something much more enjoyable
        and funny.\n\n
        WTA is intended to TV series lovers, specially to those people who want to keep track
        of their favorite shows, to stay always updated and to know about new series to watch.\n\n
        All shows data is acquired from trakt.tv (https://trakt.tv/) API.\n\n
        To report any bugs or suggestions do not hesitate to send a mail to
        david.duque.f@gmail.com
    </string>

